title: QUEEN STUDIO DISCOGRAPHY 48/24 FLAC
description:
In 2011, all of Queen studio albums were re-released, newly remastered by Bob Ludwig. 

This contains all fifteen studio albums in 48kHz 24-bit resolution, sourced from the Queen Orb USB Gift set. Converted from uncompressed WAVs to lossless FLAC with ReplayGain included (album + track). Please note this only contains the albums; the bonus tracks were unfortunately not included. 

Queen 
Queen II 
Sheer Heart Attack 
A Night At The Opera 
A Day At The Races 
News Of The World 
Jazz
